        {
            "jpName": "ナイスネイチャ",
            "enName": "Nice Nature",
            "jpText": "ぜえ、ぜえ……もうアタシは無理、疲れた……。\r\n子どもの無邪気さは心にクる……。",
            "enText": "<i>Pant… Wheeze…</i> Nope, I can't do it anymore… Their innocence \nreally hits you in the heart in more ways than one…",
